<plot>A short mockumentary that parodies 'Arts Documentaries. A dissillusioned former Canadian ballet star Jon Gibault hangs up his dance belt and becomes passionate about teaching dogs to dance. Quote: Jon Gibault: " I'll tell you what's a shame. It's a shame that in this country these animals that give us so much love have been marginalized and not allowed to create art like the rest of us . Why can't a dog get an arts grant? "</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?125561</url></doc>
